{"tid":1230414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「改變政體的顏色革命」與「煙消雲散」是一線之差","createTime":"2019-06-16T07:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:47:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"879c1fe308bec8462d67c844e82bb9a4466c032a","tid":1230414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"2010年12月17日，突尼斯一名26歲青年穆罕默德&middot;布瓦吉吉（محمد البوعزيزي&lrm;，Mohamed Bouazizi）自焚，觸發境內大規模街頭示威遊行及爭取民主活動。事件導致時任總統班&middot;阿里政權倒台，成為阿拉伯國家中第一場因人民起義導致推翻現政權的革命。<br />\n<br />\n由一個小販自焚, 觸發既示威, 喺因為人民明白到, 事件既深層原因喺政體問題<br />\n所以示威由單純自焚事件, 轉變為政體改變既訴求<br />\n<br />\n香港會唔會同樣由撤回條例, 轉為對政體改變訴求?<br />\n<br />\n遊行結尾, 喺轉向衝向禮賓府?<br />\n還是在金鐘散人?<br />\n<br />\n這是國運的十字路口"},{"pid":"ae459c93af18b0f820e14391feacec0844e1a798","tid":1230414,"uid":229955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9hCJKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9hCJKF.jpg&h=0756c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8799401534063dd02fe4ba43fc401f4172a469e","tid":1230414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6c5ef8be56554f777dc850ad86f2a6f67c5242","tid":1230414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef501ea8297d1365e49ced84e63f868189fe105","tid":1230414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca41c61e17a16a888cf57ff3bdbc2f222620380","tid":1230414,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f15b63d656549e878ff37886020b6b32f06ec26","tid":1230414,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17480c3faa1ab87c890a7e5ea50416576b2c1e90","tid":1230414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:27:59.000Z","msg":"恐怕又會MISS機會窗口<br />\n<br />\n其實歷史比香港好多機會, 不過不斷MISS"},{"pid":"82282aef23f5fa40d47f4ac68fd662ecdc85902d","tid":1230414,"uid":262690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/OMQKuU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/OMQKuU</a>"},{"pid":"a618d222689a4f72f20c15c5288556be9fa10fec","tid":1230414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82282aef23f5fa40d47f4ac68fd662ecdc85902d","tid":1230414,"uid":262690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/OMQKuU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/OMQKuU</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"如果200萬人當日一齊去禮賓府, 就真喺震撼國際媒體, 就算絕對和理非, 喺當時當刻都好有政治壓力效果<br />\n<br />\n可惜, 又一次無把握時機<br />\n<br />\n真喺倪匡《追龍》所講, 喺氣數嚟"},{"pid":"50a3f3bf214669c339ee37f81abba4589679de1d","tid":1230414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"disl